First you need create the forms in HubSpot after that HubSpot is provided iframe code,after that you will put that code to the respective website.
This is sample iframe code as HubSpot is provided:
<script charset="utf-8" type="text/javascript" src="<//js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js>"></script>
<script>
  hbspt.forms.create({
    region: "na1",
    portalId: "46522068",
    formId: "fe1f1aee-8cc2-425c-b555-22366f743e04"
  });
</script>
